<br>
&quot;I'm looking for the Queen, is she here?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenmaytha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Maytha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 96<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(8/15/02 10:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=149.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/amznqnmay/smallmaytha.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Visiting Sarmatia</span><hr size=1> Queen Maytha stayed in her hut, with her children. Her hut was big, and had many guards in front of it, to protect her. An amazon directs Ephiny to the hut with the gaurds..... <p><FONT SIZE="10"><FONT FACE="WingDings">Z</FONT>
<FONT SIZE="2"></FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/utheamazonephiny.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Amazon Ephiny</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(8/16/02 12:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=149.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The Queen</span><hr size=1> Ephiny came to Queen Maytha's hut, and stood in front of the entrance.<br>
<br>
&quot;Vasilissa Maytha? May I speak with you?&quot;<br>
<br>
She waited for Maytha to allow her to come in. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenmaytha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Maytha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 99<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(8/17/02 7:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=149.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/amznqnmay/smallmaytha.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Queen</span><hr size=1> Maytha opened the door....and let her 2 older daughters, who were just 3 and 1 years old, run out and play. As Maytha held Ella in her arms, she looks at Ephiny. &quot;Yasoo Ephiny...please come in&quot; Maytha asks her in the hut, and shuts the door when she enters. &quot;Is there anything you need?&quot; Maytha asks.... <p><FONT SIZE="10"><FONT FACE="WingDings">Z</FONT>
<FONT SIZE="2"></FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/utheamazonephiny.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Amazon Ephiny</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(8/17/02 8:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=149.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/amazonephiny/images/ephiny-herc-07.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Queen</span><hr size=1> Ephiny smiled as the children ran out of the Queen's hut and she looked back to Maytha and looked to the wee one in her arms. <br>
<br>
&quot;Very adorable.&quot;<br>
<br>
She then nodded to Maytha.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yasoo, Vasilissa. I've just recently come from the neighbouring lands of Smyrna and I was wondering if I could join your tribe.&quot;<br>
<br>
Yes, Ephiny was searching out the rest of her Athelfi. She knew she would be missed from her old tribe, but she journyed out anyway, too visit more of the lands and becoming an athelfi of the other tribes, as well as establishing her own. <p>>^< Ephiny >^<</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenmaytha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Maytha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 100<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(8/18/02 7:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=149.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/amznqnmay/smallmaytha.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Queen</span><hr size=1> Maytha listens to Ephiny and smiles. &quot;Oh...sure u can....it would be lovely to have you here&quot; Maytha smiled at her. Maytha walks over and grabs a scroll and hands it to her. &quot;Just fill this out and return it to me&quot; Maytha says.<br>
